sp. n. (mm) in comparison with those of the South American congener 
<taxonomicName genus="M." lsidName="M. venado" pageId="3" pageNumber="90" rank="species" species="venado">M. venado</taxonomicName>
(Anisyutkin, 2014).
</paragraph>
